tool_description:
Philippines Social Security OCR API allows you to onboard your customers with speed and precision.

Enable them to pre-fill their onboarding forms instantly, by just uploading or scanning their Social Security card – IDfy will digitize the document for you!
title: Philippines Social Security OCR

api_list.name: GET Call
api_list.description: Used to fetch api result using the request id received in responses.

api_list.name: Philippines Social Security OCR
api_list.description:
Philippines Social Security OCR API allows you to onboard your customers with speed and precision.

 Enable them to pre-fill their onboarding forms instantly, by just uploading or scanning their Social Security card – IDfy will digitize the document for you!

Please use the GET Call in the bundle, to obtain results for request id obtained in the response.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://philippines-social-security-ocr.p.rapidapi.com/v3/tasks/async/extract/phl_sss"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "philippines-social-security-ocr.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
